Hello! Thank you for visiting our website today.
If you have a question about an upcoming event we are having, or would like to book your own event in our Silver Fern Lounge, please call &ask to speak with a manager. It is suggested to make a reservation for any party over eight atendees at any time of any day. We can't wait to see you!
APPLICATIONS ARE DONE IN-PERSON ONLY &KIWI'S IS ALWAYS ACCEPTING. We have low turnover, however, you never know if you will happen to come in at the exact right time! Please introduce yourself to the manager on duty &they will make sure the hiring manager for your position - front of house or back of house - receives it.
Have a lovely day.
